A powerful feature of orgmode/emacs is the ability to easily and rapidly insert footnotes1 (See section ) and then easily export them, even as html.2 (See section ) You can learn all about the commands in the official manual entry.
Footnotes: ^{1 (See section )} Just like this one, using C-c C-x f
^{2 (See section )} Export as HTML and view in browser using: C-c C-e h o